An algorithm for the detection of putative G4 motifs was developed in house using Perl programing language and was applied to the reference genome of Mtb H37Rv (NC_000962.3). First, all guanine homopolymers (G-islands) were identified through pattern matching with the following line of code: (equation I)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
